From 29b0a9b6e9b125b0be015513a59db943b1fdeb78 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jianxiong Pan <jianxiong.pan@amlogic.com>
Date: Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:15:07 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] mm: add amlogic vmap stack for arm64. [1/1]

PD#SWPL-188077

Problem:
optimizate kernel stack.

Solution:
enable amlogic vmap stack.

Verify:
local.

